messages.messageBody:
I so wish we could go...I've been trying to find someone that will work for me at that powwow.
So far - not so good!
Janis
----- Original Message -----
From: kbcdlovejo@...
To: Unschooling-Discussion@yahoogroups.com
Sent: Saturday, August 09, 2003 8:52 AM
Subject: Re: [Unschooling-Discussion] conference WAS Re: Newbie Questions


In a message dated 8/9/2003 8:49:23 AM Eastern Daylight Time,
jana@... writes:


> okay....I was thinking that you/the speakers could sell them...would that
> make a difference?
>
> There are the tapes, though, right??
>

We DO sell the audiotapes. From last year too. But the idea of being
videotaped was making some of the speakers too self-conscious. I want them ON for the
attendees, NOT uncomfortable---and audiotapes are tough enough! <G>

Maybe in the future.

~Kelly
